data.description: Come see this beautifully renovated brick ranch today! Established neighborhood in River Forest Shores! Gorgeous hardwood flooring and brand new tile. Newly renovated bathrooms and eat-in kitchen with ALL NEW appliances. Cozy living room with a wood fireplace. Formal dining room for hosting holidays! HUGE back deck and yard for barbecuing! Large storage shed and plenty of parking as well. Make this your first showing before it's gone!
